# 3-Class Baseline (Biased, Trainable)
# Purpose: Near-chance start with a tiny class-aligned bias to break symmetry,
# while remaining trainable to high accuracy with the descent-like trainer.

# NEURON <id> <threshold> <leak> <resting>
# CONNECTION <from_id> <to_id> <weight>

# Sensory
NEURON S0 100.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON S1 100.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON S2 100.0 1.0 0.0

# Outputs and pool
NEURON O0 50.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON O1 50.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON O2 50.0 1.0 0.0
NEURON N0 40.0 0.8 0.0  # inhibitory pool

# Tiny class-aligned bias in feedforward (â‰ˆ +0.2 over cross)
CONNECTION S0 O0 35.2
CONNECTION S0 O1 35.0
CONNECTION S0 O2 35.0

CONNECTION S1 O0 35.0
CONNECTION S1 O1 35.2
CONNECTION S1 O2 35.0

CONNECTION S2 O0 35.0
CONNECTION S2 O1 35.0
CONNECTION S2 O2 35.2

# Pool wiring (moderate; allows WTA during/after training)
CONNECTION O0 N0 20.0
CONNECTION O1 N0 20.0
CONNECTION O2 N0 20.0

CONNECTION N0 O0 -25.0
CONNECTION N0 O1 -25.0
CONNECTION N0 O2 -25.0

